---
import BaseLayout from "../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import CTAButton from "../../components/CTAButton.astro";
import InfoCard from "../../components/InfoCard.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Cloud Security / ISSO Resume | BuiltByPCB"
  description="Cloud security, ISSO, continuous monitoring, shared responsibility, and operational control resume track for PCB."
  active="resume"
>
  <main id="top" class="bg-slate-950 px-6 py-12 text-slate-100 md:py-16">
    <section class="mx-auto max-w-5xl">
      <p class="mb-4 text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-cyan-300">
        Cloud Security / ISSO
      </p>

      <h1 class="max-w-4xl text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight md:text-6xl">
        Operational security experience applied to cloud governance, monitoring, and control assurance.
      </h1>

      <p class="mt-6 max-w-3xl text-lg leading-8 text-slate-300">
        CISSP-certified security professional building toward cloud security and ISSO roles
        by combining mission-critical operations, incident response, continuous monitoring,
        documentation discipline, and cloud security governance principles.
      </p>

      <div class="mt-8 flex flex-wrap gap-4">
        <CTAButton href="/Paul_Christian_Brown_GS13_Resume.pdf" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">
          Download Resume
        </CTAButton>

        <CTAButton href="/case-studies/cloud-monitoring" variant="secondary">
          View Cloud Case Study
        </CTAButton>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="mx-auto mt-12 max-w-5xl">
      <div class="grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-2">
        <InfoCard title="Cloud Security Strengths">
          <ul class="space-y-3">
            <li>• Shared responsibility and cloud risk governance</li>
            <li>• Identity and least-privilege concepts</li>
            <li>• Logging, monitoring, and evidence readiness</li>
            <li>• Secure configuration and baseline validation</li>
            <li>• Incident response and operational escalation</li>
            <li>• NIST/RMF-aligned control thinking</li>
            <li>• Documentation and audit traceability</li>
          </ul>
        </InfoCard>

        <InfoCard title="ISSO / Cloud Governance Profile">
          <div class="space-y-4">
            <p>
              PCB’s cloud security lane is grounded in operations: understanding how systems
              fail, how incidents are escalated, how evidence is documented, and how controls
              must remain measurable in real environments.
            </p>

            <p>
              This track is designed for ISSO, cloud security support, RMF sustainment,
              continuous monitoring, and cloud governance roles where technical operations
              and risk management intersect.
            </p>

            <p>
              Current positioning is strongest for cloud security governance and operational
              assurance, with deeper architecture depth building through CCSP and AWS/Azure labs.
            </p>
          </div>
        </InfoCard>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="mx-auto mt-12 max-w-5xl">
      <InfoCard title="Representative Cloud / ISSO-Relevant Experience">
        <div class="space-y-6">
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-cyan-300">
              Continuous Monitoring & Evidence Discipline
            </h3>
            <p class="mt-2">
              Supported monitoring workflows, escalation documentation, operational evidence,
              and after-action reporting that map directly to cloud control assurance and
              authorization sustainment.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-cyan-300">
              Incident Response & Operational Risk
            </h3>
            <p class="mt-2">
              Coordinated incident response activities in high-availability environments,
              translating technical impact into risk-aware communication and corrective action.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-cyan-300">
              Configuration, Remediation & Control Support
            </h3>
            <p class="mt-2">
              Partnered with technical teams to track remediation, validate fixes, support
              secure configuration expectations, and improve operational traceability.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </InfoCard>
    </section>

    <section class="mx-auto mt-12 max-w-5xl">
      <div class="rounded-3xl border border-cyan-300/30 bg-slate-900 p-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold">
          Best-Fit Role Targets
        </h2>

        <div class="mt-6 grid gap-4 md:grid-cols-2">
          <div class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-800 bg-slate-950 p-5 text-slate-300">
            ISSO / RMF Sustainment
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-800 bg-slate-950 p-5 text-slate-300">
            Cloud Security Analyst
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-800 bg-slate-950 p-5 text-slate-300">
            Cloud Governance / Assurance
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-800 bg-slate-950 p-5 text-slate-300">
            Continuous Monitoring / Controls Support
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-8 flex flex-wrap gap-4">
          <CTAButton href="/resume/grc-risk" variant="secondary">
            GRC / Risk Track
          </CTAButton>

          <CTAButton href="/case-studies">
            View Case Studies
          </CTAButton>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <div class="mx-auto mt-12 max-w-6xl px-6 pb-4 text-center">
      <CTAButton href="#top" variant="secondary">
        Back to Top ↑
      </CTAButton>
    </div>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>